{"openapi":"3.0.3","info":{"title":"Guardian Orchestrator API","version":"1.0.0","description":"API documentation for the Guardian orchestrator gateway. The mobile authentication endpoint fans out credentials to deployed workspaces registered in the orchestrator database, preferring each registered backend ingress URL and falling back to Docker service DNS when needed."},"servers":[{"url":"http://localhost:9168","description":"Local orchestrator"}],"tags":[{"name":"Mobile Auth","description":"Mobile authentication gateway endpoints"},{"name":"Workspace Deployment","description":"Workspace deployment endpoints"},{"name":"Documentation","description":"API documentation endpoints"}],"paths":{"/mobile/auth/login":{"post":{"tags":["Mobile Auth"],"summary":"Authenticate a mobile user against registered workspaces","description":"Receives mobile credentials, attempts login against each deployed workspace registered in the orchestrator database using its backend ingress URL or registered backend service DNS, and returns the tokens for every workspace that authenticates successfully. Credential values are never returned in the response.","operationId":"mobileAuthLogin","requestBody":{"required":true,"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/MobileAuthLoginRequest"},"examples":{"password":{"summary":"Login with password","value":{"email":"user@example.com","password":"secret"}},"clave":{"summary":"Login with clave alias","value":{"email":"user@example.com","clave":"secret"}}}}}},"responses":{"200":{"description":"At least one deployed workspace authenticated the user.","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/MobileAuthLoginSuccess"}}}},"400":{"description":"Missing email or password/clave.","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse"},"example":{"code":400,"error":"email and password are required"}}}},"401":{"description":"No registered deployed workspace authenticated the credentials.","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/MobileAuthLoginFailure"}}}},"500":{"description":"The authentication gateway could not read the registry or complete the fan-out.","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse"},"example":{"code":500,"error":"authentication gateway unavailable"}}}}}}},"/mobile/workspaces/summary":{"post":{"tags":["Mobile Auth"],"summary":"Aggregate workspace summary metrics for mobile sessions","description":"Receives workspace sessions previously returned by /mobile/auth/login, validates each token against the corresponding deployed workspace backend, and returns partial monitoring metrics. This endpoint does not make user authorization or SuperAdmin decisions; it only aggregates data for the sessions supplied by the mobile app.","operationId":"mobileWorkspacesSummary","requestBody":{"required":true,"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/MobileWorkspaceSummaryRequest"},"example":{"sessions":[{"workspace":"jcae","token":"eyJhbGciOi..."}]}}}},"responses":{"200":{"description":"Workspace summaries and per-workspace failures. Invalid tokens are reported in failures and are not included in workspaces.","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/MobileWorkspaceSummaryResponse"}}}},"400":{"description":"Invalid request body, such as missing or empty sessions.","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse"},"example":{"code":400,"error":"sessions must be a non-empty array"}}}},"500":{"description":"The summary gateway could not read the registry or complete the aggregation.","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse"},"example":{"code":500,"error":"workspace summary gateway unavailable"}}}}}}},"/mobile/workspaces/alerts/dashboard":{"post":{"tags":["Mobile Auth"],"summary":"Aggregate alerts dashboard charts for mobile sessions","description":"Receives workspace sessions previously returned by /mobile/auth/login and calls the real workspace backend chart endpoint for each deployed workspace. This endpoint does not implement permission or SuperAdmin logic; /mobile/auth/login controls access. Time can be requested with a preset (`last_1h`, `last_24h`, `last_7d`) or with a custom interval using `from` and/or `to` in ISO 8601 format. When `from` or `to` is provided, the backend treats the range as a custom interval and those values take priority over `timePreset`.","operationId":"mobileWorkspacesAlertsDashboard","requestBody":{"required":true,"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/MobileAlertsDashboardRequest"},"examples":{"presetLast24h":{"summary":"Use a predefined time preset","description":"Valid presets are `last_1h`, `last_24h`, and `last_7d`. Do not send `from` or `to` when using only a preset.","value":{"sessions":[{"workspace":"jcae","token":"eyJhbGciOi..."}],"timePreset":"last_24h","timezone":"America/Lima","deviceIds":[],"limit":10}},"customInterval":{"summary":"Use a custom date/time interval","description":"Send `from` and `to` as ISO 8601 date-time values. Custom intervals take priority over `timePreset`; you may omit `timePreset` or set it to `custom` for readability.","value":{"sessions":[{"workspace":"jcae","token":"eyJhbGciOi..."}],"timePreset":"custom","from":"2026-05-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-05-27T23:59:59.999Z","timezone":"America/Lima","deviceIds":[],"limit":10}}}}}},"responses":{"200":{"description":"Alerts dashboard charts and per-workspace failures. A workspace is included only when totalAlerts succeeds; individual chart failures are reported as anomalies with that chart set to null.","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/MobileAlertsDashboardResponse"}}}},"400":{"description":"Invalid request body, such as missing sessions or invalid filters.","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse"},"example":{"code":400,"error":"sessions must be a non-empty array"}}}},"500":{"description":"The alerts dashboard gateway could not read the registry or complete the aggregation.","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse"},"example":{"code":500,"error":"alerts dashboard gateway unavailable"}}}}}}},"/mobile/workspaces/events":{"post":{"tags":["Mobile Auth"],"summary":"Fetch generated events for mobile workspace sessions","description":"Receives workspace sessions previously returned by /mobile/auth/login. For each deployed workspace, the gateway first validates the supplied JWT against the protected backend endpoint GET /api/v1/users, then calls the mapped legacy event endpoint with the same Authorization header. The gateway does not decide permissions. `from` and `to` are required ISO 8601 date-time values and are converted with `timezone` to the legacy backend format `YYYY/MM/DD_HH-mm-ss`.","operationId":"mobileWorkspacesEvents","requestBody":{"required":true,"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/MobileWorkspaceEventsRequest"},"example":{"sessions":[{"workspace":"jcae","token":"eyJhbGciOi..."}],"eventType":"alert","from":"2026-05-27T00:00:00-05:00","to":"2026-05-27T23:59:59-05:00","timezone":"America/Lima","page":1,"limit":30,"filters":{"deviceId":"all","tags":[],"plate_char":"","rulesId":[],"traineds":[]}}}}},"responses":{"200":{"description":"Per-workspace event results and failures. Invalid tokens are reported in failures and are not included in workspaces.","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/MobileWorkspaceEventsResponse"}}}},"400":{"description":"Invalid request body, such as missing from/to, unsupported event type, or invalid pagination.","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse"},"example":{"code":400,"error":"from is required"}}}},"500":{"description":"The events gateway could not read the registry or complete the aggregation.","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse"},"example":{"code":500,"error":"workspace events gateway unavailable"}}}}}}},"/mobile/workspaces/search":{"post":{"tags":["Mobile Auth"],"summary":"Search alerts and smart events across supplied workspace sessions","description":"Receives only the workspace sessions previously returned by /mobile/auth/login, validates each token with GET /api/v1/users, then searches the real backend endpoints POST /api/v1/alerts/find and/or POST /api/v1/smart_event/find. Backend-supported filters are forwarded directly: deviceId, full datetime range, plate_char, and tags. Criteria that the backend does not expose directly are mapped to tags or reported in anomalies; the gateway does not discover extra workspaces and never returns tokens.","operationId":"mobileWorkspacesSearch","requestBody":{"required":true,"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/MobileWorkspaceSearchRequest"},"example":{"sessions":[{"workspace":"jcae","token":"eyJhbGciOi..."}],"query":{"faceName":"Juan","plate":"ABC123","listName":"VIP","smartEventName":"intrusion"},"filters":{"analyticType":"all","deviceId":"all","from":"2026-05-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-05-28T23:59:59.999Z","timezone":"UTC","hourFrom":"08:00","hourTo":"18:00"},"eventTypes":["alert","smart_event"],"page":1,"limit":30}}}},"responses":{"200":{"description":"Per-workspace search results and failures. Invalid tokens are reported in failures and are not included in workspaces.","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/MobileWorkspaceSearchResponse"}}}},"400":{"description":"Invalid request body, such as missing sessions, unsupported eventTypes, invalid analyticType, or invalid time filters.","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse"},"example":{"code":400,"error":"sessions must be a non-empty array"}}}},"500":{"description":"The search gateway could not read the registry or complete the aggregation.","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse"},"example":{"code":500,"error":"workspace search gateway unavailable"}}}}}}},"/mobile/workspaces/events/classification":{"post":{"tags":["Mobile Auth"],"summary":"Classify Alert or SmartEvent records for mobile workspace sessions","description":"Validates each supplied workspace session with GET /api/v1/users, then proxies confirm, ignore, or false_positive to the workspace backend classification endpoint. The gateway preserves the backend payload shape `{ eventId, user: { user: ... } }` and does not create incidents, descriptions, device actions, websocket events, or Telegram notifications itself; those side effects remain backend-owned.","operationId":"mobileWorkspacesEventClassification","requestBody":{"required":true,"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/MobileEventClassificationRequest"},"example":{"sessions":[{"workspace":"jcae","token":"eyJhbGciOi..."}],"eventType":"smart_event","eventId":44,"classification":"confirm","user":{"id":5,"first_name":"Alice","last_name":"Guardian","Username":"aguardian"}}}}},"responses":{"200":{"description":"Per-workspace backend classification results and failures. Invalid tokens are rejected before classification forwarding.","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/MobileEventClassificationResponse"}}}},"400":{"description":"Invalid request body, unsupported event type, or unsupported classification.","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse"},"example":{"code":400,"error":"classification is required and must be confirm, ignore, or false_positive"}}}},"500":{"description":"The classification gateway could not read the registry or complete the aggregation.","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse"},"example":{"code":500,"error":"workspace classification gateway unavailable"}}}}}}},"/mobile/workspaces/devices":{"post":{"tags":["Mobile Auth"],"summary":"Fetch devices for mobile workspace sessions","description":"Receives one or more workspace sessions previously returned by /mobile/auth/login. Clients can request devices for multiple workspaces in the same request by sending several items in the `sessions` array. For each deployed workspace, the gateway first validates the supplied JWT against the protected backend endpoint GET /api/v1/users, then calls GET /api/v1/device/all and GET /api/v1/device/runtime-status with the same Authorization header. The gateway does not decide permissions. `rtspStatus` and `recording.active` are merged from the backend runtime-status rows when available; otherwise the device is still returned with null runtime fields and a runtimeStatus anomaly.","operationId":"mobileWorkspacesDevices","requestBody":{"required":true,"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/MobileWorkspaceDevicesRequest"},"example":{"sessions":[{"workspace":"jcae","token":"eyJhbGciOi..."},{"workspace":"verifydns","token":"eyJhbGciOi..."}]}}}},"responses":{"200":{"description":"Per-workspace device lists and failures. Invalid tokens are reported in failures and are not included in workspaces.","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/MobileWorkspaceDevicesResponse"}}}},"400":{"description":"Invalid request body, such as missing or empty sessions.","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse"},"example":{"code":400,"error":"sessions must be a non-empty array"}}}},"500":{"description":"The devices gateway could not read the registry or complete the aggregation.","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse"},"example":{"code":500,"error":"workspace devices gateway unavailable"}}}}}}},"/mobile/workspaces/alarms/configurations":{"post":{"tags":["Mobile Auth"],"summary":"List alarm configurations for mobile workspace sessions","description":"Validates each supplied workspace token with GET /api/v1/users, then proxies GET /api/v1/alarm to each workspace backend.","operationId":"mobileWorkspaceAlarmConfigurations","requestBody":{"required":true,"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/MobileWorkspaceSummaryRequest"},"examples":{"jcae":{"summary":"List configurations for jcae","value":{"sessions":[{"workspace":"jcae","token":"eyJhbGciOi..."}]}},"verifydns":{"summary":"List configurations for verifydns","value":{"sessions":[{"workspace":"verifydns","token":"eyJhbGciOi..."}]}}}}}},"responses":{"200":{"$ref":"#/components/responses/MobileAlarmGatewayResponse"},"400":{"$ref":"#/components/responses/BadRequest"},"500":{"$ref":"#/components/responses/GatewayUnavailable"}}}},"/mobile/workspaces/alarms/configurations/detail":{"post":{"tags":["Mobile Auth"],"summary":"Get one alarm configuration detail","description":"Validates each supplied workspace token with GET /api/v1/users, then proxies GET /api/v1/alarm/{alarmId}/ to each workspace backend.","operationId":"mobileWorkspaceAlarmConfigurationDetail","requestBody":{"required":true,"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/MobileAlarmDetailRequest"},"example":{"sessions":[{"workspace":"jcae","token":"eyJhbGciOi..."}],"alarmId":12}}}},"responses":{"200":{"$ref":"#/components/responses/MobileAlarmGatewayResponse"},"400":{"$ref":"#/components/responses/BadRequest"},"500":{"$ref":"#/components/responses/GatewayUnavailable"}}}},"/mobile/workspaces/alarms/configurations/update":{"post":{"tags":["Mobile Auth"],"summary":"Update alarm and/or action configuration","description":"Validates each supplied workspace token with GET /api/v1/users. When `alarm` is present, proxies PUT /api/v1/alarm/{alarmId}/. When `action` is present, proxies PUT /api/v1/alarm/action/{action.id}/. Unknown mutation fields are rejected with 400.","operationId":"mobileWorkspaceAlarmConfigurationUpdate","requestBody":{"required":true,"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/MobileAlarmUpdateRequest"},"example":{"sessions":[{"workspace":"jcae","token":"eyJhbGciOi..."}],"alarmId":12,"alarm":{"sound":3},"action":{"id":44,"issound":true,"isalert":true,"manual_confirmation":false,"ismodal":true,"timeout":30}}}}},"responses":{"200":{"$ref":"#/components/responses/MobileAlarmGatewayResponse"},"400":{"$ref":"#/components/responses/BadRequest"},"500":{"$ref":"#/components/responses/GatewayUnavailable"}}}},"/mobile/workspaces/alarms/configurations/polygons/update":{"post":{"tags":["Mobile Auth"],"summary":"Update alarm ROI polygons","description":"Validates each supplied workspace token with GET /api/v1/users, then proxies PUT /api/v1/alarm/roi/{roiId}/ for each polygon. Unknown polygon fields are rejected with 400.","operationId":"mobileWorkspaceAlarmPolygonsUpdate","requestBody":{"required":true,"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/MobileAlarmPolygonsUpdateRequest"},"example":{"sessions":[{"workspace":"jcae","token":"eyJhbGciOi..."}],"polygons":[{"roiId":9,"state":true,"points":"[[0.12,0.18],[0.86,0.18],[0.86,0.74],[0.12,0.74]]"}]}}}},"responses":{"200":{"$ref":"#/components/responses/MobileAlarmGatewayResponse"},"400":{"$ref":"#/components/responses/BadRequest"},"500":{"$ref":"#/components/responses/GatewayUnavailable"}}}},"/mobile/workspaces/alarms/sounds":{"post":{"tags":["Mobile Auth"],"summary":"List alarm sounds","description":"Validates each supplied workspace token with GET /api/v1/users, then proxies GET /api/v1/sounds to each workspace backend.","operationId":"mobileWorkspaceAlarmSounds","requestBody":{"required":true,"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/MobileWorkspaceSummaryRequest"},"example":{"sessions":[{"workspace":"jcae","token":"eyJhbGciOi..."}]}}}},"responses":{"200":{"$ref":"#/components/responses/MobileAlarmGatewayResponse"},"400":{"$ref":"#/components/responses/BadRequest"},"500":{"$ref":"#/components/responses/GatewayUnavailable"}}}},"/":{"post":{"tags":["Workspace Deployment"],"summary":"Deploy a workspace","description":"Starts deployment for a workspace and registers deployment state in the orchestrator database.","operationId":"deployWorkspace","requestBody":{"required":true,"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/WorkspaceDeployRequest"}}}},"responses":{"200":{"description":"Workspace deployment started and completed successfully.","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/WorkspaceDeployResponse"}}}},"400":{"description":"Invalid workspace slug."},"500":{"description":"Deployment failed."}}}},"/test":{"post":{"tags":["Workspace Deployment"],"summary":"Deploy a workspace through the legacy test route","description":"Legacy alias for workspace deployment. It uses the same request body as POST /. ","operationId":"deployWorkspaceTest","requestBody":{"required":true,"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/WorkspaceDeployRequest"}}}},"responses":{"200":{"description":"Workspace deployment completed successfully."},"400":{"description":"Invalid workspace slug."},"500":{"description":"Deployment failed."}}}},"/openapi.json":{"get":{"tags":["Documentation"],"summary":"Return the OpenAPI specification","operationId":"getOpenApiSpec","security":[{"docsBearerAuth":[]}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"OpenAPI JSON document.","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"type":"object"}}}},"401":{"description":"Missing or invalid documentation token."}}}},"/docs/openapi.json":{"get":{"tags":["Documentation"],"summary":"Return the OpenAPI specification for Swagger UI","operationId":"getDocsOpenApiSpec","security":[{"docsBearerAuth":[]}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"OpenAPI JSON document loaded by /docs.","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"type":"object"}}}},"401":{"description":"Missing or invalid documentation token."}}}},"/docs":{"get":{"tags":["Documentation"],"summary":"Open Swagger UI documentation","operationId":"getSwaggerUi","security":[{"docsBearerAuth":[]}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"Swagger UI HTML page that loads /docs/openapi.json.","content":{"text/html":{"schema":{"type":"string"}}}},"401":{"description":"Missing or invalid documentation token."}}}}},"components":{"securitySchemes":{"docsBearerAuth":{"type":"http","scheme":"bearer","bearerFormat":"opaque"}},"requestBodies":{"MobileWorkspaceSessions":{"required":true,"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/MobileWorkspaceSummaryRequest"}}}}},"responses":{"MobileAlarmGatewayResponse":{"description":"Per-workspace alarm proxy results and failures.","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/MobileAlarmGatewayResponse"},"examples":{"configurations":{"summary":"Alarm configurations returned for two workspaces","value":{"workspaces":[{"workspace":"jcae","status":"deployed","backendUrl":"http://jcae.guardian.imperium.pe:8088","configurations":[{"id":12,"name":"Main gate intrusion","state":true,"sound":3,"actions":[{"id":44,"issound":true,"isalert":true,"manual_confirmation":false,"ismodal":true,"timeout":30}]}]},{"workspace":"verifydns","status":"deployed","backendUrl":"http://verifydns.guardian.imperium.pe:8088","configurations":[]}],"failures":[]}},"detail":{"summary":"Alarm configuration detail by alarmId","value":{"workspaces":[{"workspace":"jcae","status":"deployed","backendUrl":"http://jcae.guardian.imperium.pe:8088","alarm":{"id":12,"name":"Main gate intrusion","state":true,"sound":3,"roi":[{"id":9,"state":true,"points":"[[0.12,0.18],[0.86,0.18],[0.86,0.74],[0.12,0.74]]"}]}}],"failures":[]}},"update":{"summary":"Alarm and action update result","value":{"workspaces":[{"workspace":"jcae","status":"deployed","backendUrl":"http://jcae.guardian.imperium.pe:8088","result":{"alarm":{"id":12,"sound":3},"action":{"id":44,"issound":true,"isalert":true,"manual_confirmation":false,"ismodal":true,"timeout":30}}}],"failures":[]}},"polygonsUpdate":{"summary":"ROI polygon update result","value":{"workspaces":[{"workspace":"jcae","status":"deployed","backendUrl":"http://jcae.guardian.imperium.pe:8088","polygons":[{"roiId":9,"result":{"id":9,"state":true,"points":"[[0.12,0.18],[0.86,0.18],[0.86,0.74],[0.12,0.74]]"}}]}],"failures":[]}},"sounds":{"summary":"Available alarm sounds","value":{"workspaces":[{"workspace":"jcae","status":"deployed","backendUrl":"http://jcae.guardian.imperium.pe:8088","sounds":[{"id":3,"name":"Siren","file":"siren.mp3"},{"id":4,"name":"Beep","file":"beep.mp3"}]}],"failures":[]}},"partialFailure":{"summary":"One workspace failed while others succeeded","value":{"workspaces":[{"workspace":"jcae","status":"deployed","backendUrl":"http://jcae.guardian.imperium.pe:8088","configurations":[]}],"failures":[{"workspace":"verifydns","status":"invalid_token"}]}}}}}},"BadRequest":{"description":"Invalid request body.","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse"}}}},"GatewayUnavailable":{"description":"The gateway could not read the registry or complete the aggregation.","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse"}}}}},"schemas":{"MobileAuthLoginRequest":{"type":"object","required":["email"],"properties":{"email":{"type":"string","format":"email","example":"user@example.com"},"password":{"type":"string","format":"password","description":"User password. Either password or clave is required.","example":"secret"},"clave":{"type":"string","format":"password","description":"Alias accepted by the gateway for password.","example":"secret"}},"oneOf":[{"required":["password"]},{"required":["clave"]}]},"MobileAuthLoginSuccess":{"type":"object","required":["results"],"properties":{"results":{"type":"array","items":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/MobileAuthWorkspaceSession"}}}},"MobileAuthWorkspaceSession":{"type":"object","required":["workspace","token","jwt","user"],"properties":{"workspace":{"type":"string","example":"demo"},"token":{"type":"string","description":"JWT returned by the workspace backend."},"jwt":{"type":"string","description":"Same value as token, preserved for compatibility with the workspace backend response."},"role":{"nullable":true,"oneOf":[{"type":"string"},{"type":"number"},{"type":"object","additionalProperties":true}],"example":"admin"},"user":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/BasicUser"}}},"BasicUser":{"type":"object","description":"Sanitized user object returned by the workspace backend. Password, clave, token, and hash-like fields are removed.","additionalProperties":true,"properties":{"id":{"type":"integer","example":1},"email":{"type":"string","format":"email","example":"user@example.com"},"name":{"type":"string","example":"Jane Doe"}}},"MobileAuthLoginFailure":{"type":"object","required":["code","error","failures"],"properties":{"code":{"type":"integer","example":401},"error":{"type":"string","example":"authentication failed for registered workspaces"},"failures":{"type":"array","items":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/WorkspaceAuthFailure"}}}},"MobileWorkspaceSummaryRequest":{"type":"object","required":["sessions"],"properties":{"sessions":{"type":"array","minItems":1,"description":"One or more workspace sessions. Include multiple items to fetch devices from multiple deployed workspaces in one request.","items":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/MobileWorkspaceSummarySession"}}}},"MobileWorkspaceSummarySession":{"type":"object","required":["workspace"],"properties":{"workspace":{"type":"string","example":"jcae"},"token":{"type":"string","description":"JWT returned by /mobile/auth/login for this workspace. Either token or jwt is required."},"jwt":{"type":"string","description":"Alias accepted when token is omitted."}},"oneOf":[{"required":["token"]},{"required":["jwt"]}]},"MobileWorkspaceSummaryResponse":{"type":"object","required":["workspaces","failures"],"properties":{"workspaces":{"type":"array","items":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/MobileWorkspaceSummary"}},"failures":{"type":"array","items":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/MobileWorkspaceSummaryFailure"}}}},"MobileWorkspaceSummary":{"type":"object","required":["workspace","status","backendUrl","metrics","adminAccess","anomalies"],"properties":{"workspace":{"type":"string","example":"jcae"},"status":{"type":"string","example":"deployed"},"backendUrl":{"type":"string","example":"http://jcae.guardian.imperium.pe:8088"},"metrics":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/MobileWorkspaceMetrics"},"adminAccess":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/MobileWorkspaceAdminAccess"},"anomalies":{"type":"array","items":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/MobileWorkspaceAnomaly"}}}},"MobileWorkspaceMetrics":{"type":"object","required":["usersCount","camerasCount","onlineCamerasCount","health","queue"],"properties":{"usersCount":{"type":"integer","nullable":true,"example":4},"camerasCount":{"type":"integer","nullable":true,"example":18},"onlineCamerasCount":{"type":"integer","nullable":true,"description":"Currently null because the backend has no reliable online camera aggregate."},"health":{"type":"object","nullable":true,"additionalProperties":true},"queue":{"type":"object","nullable":true,"additionalProperties":true}}},"MobileWorkspaceAdminAccess":{"type":"object","required":["enabled","token"],"properties":{"enabled":{"type":"boolean","example":true},"token":{"type":"string","description":"The same token provided for this workspace session."}}},"MobileWorkspaceAnomaly":{"type":"object","required":["metric","status"],"properties":{"metric":{"type":"string","example":"onlineCamerasCount"},"status":{"type":"string","example":"unsupported"},"detail":{"type":"string","nullable":true,"example":"Backend does not expose live RTSP status"}}},"MobileWorkspaceSummaryFailure":{"type":"object","required":["workspace","status"],"properties":{"workspace":{"type":"string","example":"jcae"},"status":{"type":"string","enum":["invalid_token","workspace_not_found","workspace_not_deployed","unreachable","backend_error"],"example":"invalid_token"}}},"MobileAlertsDashboardRequest":{"type":"object","required":["sessions"],"properties":{"sessions":{"type":"array","minItems":1,"items":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/MobileWorkspaceSummarySession"}},"timePreset":{"type":"string","nullable":true,"enum":["last_1h","last_24h","last_7d","custom"],"description":"Predefined time range for the charts. Use `last_1h`, `last_24h`, or `last_7d` for automatic relative windows. Use `custom` only as a readable label when also sending `from` and/or `to`. If `from` or `to` is present, the backend uses the custom interval instead of the preset.","example":"last_24h"},"from":{"type":"string","nullable":true,"format":"date-time","description":"Start of a custom interval in ISO 8601 format. Example: `2026-05-01T00:00:00.000Z`. If provided, it takes priority over `timePreset`."},"to":{"type":"string","nullable":true,"format":"date-time","description":"End of a custom interval in ISO 8601 format. Example: `2026-05-27T23:59:59.999Z`. If provided, it takes priority over `timePreset`."},"timezone":{"type":"string","nullable":true,"description":"IANA timezone used by the backend to resolve and label the chart window. Default recommended value for this deployment is `America/Lima`.","example":"America/Lima"},"deviceIds":{"type":"array","items":{"type":"string"},"default":[]},"limit":{"type":"integer","nullable":true,"description":"Maximum number of grouped chart items returned by charts that support grouping, such as alerts by device.","example":10}}},"MobileAlertsDashboardResponse":{"type":"object","required":["workspaces","failures"],"properties":{"workspaces":{"type":"array","items":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/MobileAlertsDashboardWorkspace"}},"failures":{"type":"array","items":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/MobileWorkspaceSummaryFailure"}}}},"MobileAlertsDashboardWorkspace":{"type":"object","required":["workspace","status","backendUrl","charts","anomalies"],"properties":{"workspace":{"type":"string","example":"jcae"},"status":{"type":"string","example":"deployed"},"backendUrl":{"type":"string","example":"http://jcae.guardian.imperium.pe:8088"},"charts":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/MobileAlertsDashboardCharts"},"anomalies":{"type":"array","items":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/MobileAlertsDashboardAnomaly"}}}},"MobileAlertsDashboardCharts":{"type":"object","required":["totalAlerts","attendedAlerts","effectiveOperationPercentage","unresolvedAlerts","classifiedAlerts","alertsByDevice","operatorActionTime"],"properties":{"totalAlerts":{"type":"object","nullable":true,"additionalProperties":true},"attendedAlerts":{"type":"object","nullable":true,"additionalProperties":true},"effectiveOperationPercentage":{"type":"object","nullable":true,"additionalProperties":true},"unresolvedAlerts":{"type":"object","nullable":true,"additionalProperties":true},"classifiedAlerts":{"type":"object","nullable":true,"additionalProperties":true},"alertsByDevice":{"type":"object","nullable":true,"additionalProperties":true},"operatorActionTime":{"type":"object","nullable":true,"additionalProperties":true}}},"MobileAlertsDashboardAnomaly":{"type":"object","required":["chart","status"],"properties":{"chart":{"type":"string","example":"alertsByDevice"},"metric":{"type":"string","nullable":true,"example":"alerts_by_device"},"status":{"type":"string","example":"backend_error"}}},"MobileWorkspaceEventsRequest":{"type":"object","required":["sessions","eventType","from","to","timezone"],"properties":{"sessions":{"type":"array","minItems":1,"items":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/MobileWorkspaceSummarySession"}},"eventType":{"type":"string","description":"Event type alias. Supported mappings: alert, alerts, Alert -> POST /api/v1/alerts/find?page=N; smart_event, smartevent, smartEvent, SmartEvent -> POST /api/v1/smart_event/find?page=N; lpr, LPR -> POST /api/v1/lpr/find?page=N; face, Face -> POST /api/v1/face/find